resources.string: Hi, this is Netology! We started with courses about online marketing. Then they grew up in the University of Internet professions: they taught designers, analysts, programmers, managers, marketers… We continue to grow. Today we give knowledge not only to beginners, but also to those who have been in the profession for a long time. Netology helps to grow at all stages of a career — to gain knowledge at the start and to open new heights. Our mission is to help us embark on the path of growth and start a chain of changes.
